ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#65: FILE: drivers/hwmon/smsc47m1.c:588:
+	if ((err = device_create_file(dev, &dev_attr_name)))

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

